    "Hierarchical AnalysisTo measure the quality of the topic hierarchy, we use two measures proposed in [37]: topic specialization and hierarchical affinity.",
    "Table 2 Top 10 words per topic produced by LDA on BBC corpus The best results are in bold Topics year, people, time, world, years, game, government, technology, music, way People, year, time, film, government, world, number, way, game, year year, company, firm, years, government, week, economy, people, growth, world Year, people, time, game, film, world, years, number, club, wales year, people, government, time, election, labor, years, party, plans, music • Topic Specialization measures the distance of a topic's probability distribution over terms from the general probability distribution of all terms in the corpus given by their occurrence frequency."
